      "affectedComponent": "37MYJCZ1V9-439T",
      "impact": "",
      "mitigationPath": "",
      "decisionRationale": "Availability target: 99.9% (aligns with Microsoft's published Azure Cache for Redis Premium SLA for zone-redundant deployments in East US 2). Architecture: Premium tier with zone redundancy. A cache outage degrades entitlement-check latency (falls back to direct Postgres reads) but does not cause incorrect entitlement decisions or downtime. Monitoring: Datadog Redis integration tracks memory pressure, hit ratio, and connected client count. These declarations satisfy SLA-01's requirement to declare an availability target and identify the monitoring used to measure conformance.\n",
