      "mitigationPath": "",
      "decisionRationale": "Snowflake's multi-cluster warehouse architecture provides automatic cluster failover within the Azure East US 2 region. The BI consumption warehouse has auto-scaling enabled (multi-cluster); the ELT load warehouse scales vertically. In-region node failures are handled transparently by Snowflake's platform without operator intervention. Cross-region HA is addressed in the DR-01 recoverability record (cross-region clone). These mechanisms satisfy DR-02's requirement for backup storage in a separate region or availability zone.\n",
      "relatedDecisionRecords": [
        "5T6Z38JS60-H8WK"
      ],
