      "decisionRationale": "RTO: 4 hours (cross-region clone restore). RPO: 24 hours (last successful nightly clone). Recovery strategy: Snowflake Time Travel (7-day window) handles accidental deletion and logical corruption within the primary account. A weekly cross-region database clone to a secondary Snowflake account in a different Azure region provides catastrophic-loss recovery. Recovery procedures are documented and the cross-region clone restore process is tested during the annual DR exercise.\n",
