      "impact": "",
      "mitigationPath": "",
      "decisionRationale": "RTO: 8 hours (re-run extraction DAGs for the affected partition). RPO: 24 hours (one missed nightly load). Recovery strategy: ADLS soft-delete (14-day retention window) is the primary recovery mechanism for accidental deletion. Because raw landing data is re-derivable by re-running each source product's extraction job, the landing zone is treated as a cache of extraction, not a sole system of record. Full partition loss recovery is therefore a pipeline re-run rather than a restore operation. These objectives have been reviewed and accepted by the Data & Analytics team.\n",
