      "decisionRationale": "OS: Ubuntu 22.04 LTS \u2014 Microsoft mainstream support through April 2027 via the AKS-supported node image channel. Compute: Azure Standard_D-series v5 VM SKU \u2014 currently in mainstream support with no announced end-of-life date. Patch cadence: the AKS NodeImage auto-upgrade channel is enabled on a weekly maintenance window, automatically applying OS and kubelet patches without manual operator action. Neither component is past its vendor's end-of-extended-support date. These declarations satisfy VM-01's requirement for a documented patch cadence and confirmed lifecycle status.\n",
